<%= @event_email.subject %>

<% if @event_email.body.present? %>
<%= @event_email.body.to_plain_text %>
<% else %>
Hi <%= @user.display_name || 'there' %>!

This is a reminder about your upcoming event:

<%= @event.name %>

When: <%= @event.date.strftime('%A, %B %d, %Y') %>
<% if @event.start_time %>
Time: <%= @event.start_time.strftime('%I:%M %p') %> - <%= @event.end_time&.strftime('%I:%M %p') %>
<% end %>
Where: <%= @event.location.name %>
<%= @event.location.address %>

<% if @seat && @seat.hero %>
Your Hero: <%= @seat.hero.name %>
<% end %>

<% if @seat && @seat.game %>
Your Game Master: <%= @seat.game.gm.display_name %>
<% end %>

We're looking forward to seeing you there!
<% end %>

View Event Details: <%= event_url(@event) %>
